# Echoroo dev Redis ACL file (006-permissions-redesign, NFR-007).
#
# The default user is disabled (no commands allowed, no password) to force
# all clients to authenticate as the `echoroo` user via AUTH.
#
# Format reference: https://redis.io/docs/management/security/acl/
user default off nopass resetchannels -@all
user echoroo on >echoroo-dev-redis-password ~* &* +@all
